{"tid":177403,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"TG減肥group","createTime":"2017-03-28T23:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T18:23:13.000Z","uid":13752,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ca2f68e0ace0bdf569d400d7ed80dda9fc92c0","tid":177403,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"想開減肥小型Group，只限絲打，預5至6人左右。<br />\n太多人怕控制唔到，都擔心會愈黎愈靜。<br />\n真係肥先好入黎，想減10kg或以上嘅，瘦底扮肥死埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入group條件：<br />\n每1-2日運動30分鐘或以上，無呢個恆心唔好加入。<br />\n<br />\n每次做完運動都匯報，其他group友鼓勵一下。<br />\n目的係想多啲正能量，多個人支持你做起上黎都會落力啲！又可以keep住做！<br />\n<br />\n有人超過1-2日無運動大家會督促佢運動。<br />\n我認真想減肥，唔係玩下講下就算，無恆心就唔好入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗減肥，想識多幾個朋友，平時都可以傾下計。<br />\n一齊訂立目標，減肥成功夏天一齊著背心短褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed235748f8987260a26805d5d7228754a36c1984","tid":177403,"uid":65918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:44:53.000Z","msg":"@tomatopotatochips<br />\n利申絲"},{"pid":"6b4bfc74b0557c1028d1815ee6d0090bf7eae470","tid":177403,"uid":87238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:53:34.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你可以pm我麻？"},{"pid":"7089a79d22dfd58e50e903076f6acc36c03fe1d9","tid":177403,"uid":32175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"@vincentlam0320"},{"pid":"80e5a817de151a2d5035a068d326d697cfb07bf0","tid":177403,"uid":44102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"@iloke"},{"pid":"52ce66627f55ee01644fe00e3907a5dff9be9d8a","tid":177403,"uid":32175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>@vincentlam0320</blockquote